('jamie',
 'Jamie',
 'Privacy-first AI meeting assistant that takes notes without joining the call',
 'Jamie is an AI meeting notetaker designed for privacy-conscious users and teams in regulated industries. Unlike most AI meeting tools that require a bot to join the call, Jamie runs locally on the user''s device and processes audio without sending the raw meeting audio to a cloud server. The app listens to the system audio, transcribes in real time, and generates a structured summary with action items, decisions, and key topics organised by section. Jamie supports over 15 languages and produces summaries that maintain the structure of the conversation rather than flattening everything into bullet points. Because Jamie does not join the meeting as a participant, other attendees are never notified that AI is transcribing - useful for external client meetings, interviews, and one-on-ones where adding a bot would feel intrusive. The free plan allows 10 meetings per month with full feature access.',
 NULL,
