('sembly-ai',
 'Sembly AI',
 'AI team assistant that attends meetings and identifies risks, decisions, and tasks',
 'Sembly AI positions itself as a team-level meeting assistant rather than just a personal notetaker. When Sembly attends a meeting, it produces a transcript, summary, and action items - standard for the category - but also applies AI analysis to identify risks mentioned in the conversation, decisions that were made, and questions that were raised but not answered. The Smart Summaries feature organises meeting output by type of content rather than chronologically, so the reader can jump directly to the decisions section, the action items, or the open questions without reading through the whole meeting narrative. Sembly integrates with Jira, Asana, Trello, and Linear for direct task creation from meeting action items. The platform supports 48 languages and works across Zoom, Google Meet, Microsoft Teams, and Webex. Team workspaces let managers see summaries from all team meetings in one view, useful for staying across multiple projects without attending every standup.',
