('meetgeek',
 'MeetGeek',
 'Automatic meeting recorder with AI highlights and team meeting library',
 'MeetGeek is an automatic meeting recorder and AI assistant that builds a searchable library of every meeting a team has. The tool joins video calls automatically based on calendar invitations, records and transcribes the session, and generates an AI summary with action items and highlights. The meeting library becomes a searchable archive: team members can search for a topic across all past meetings and find the relevant moment, rather than trying to remember which call covered what. MeetGeek supports over 30 meeting templates for different meeting types - sales calls, customer discovery, team retrospectives, one-on-ones - each with a customised summary structure that captures the information most relevant to that meeting type. The platform integrates with Notion, Slack, HubSpot, Salesforce, and Zapier for automatic distribution of summaries. MeetGeek is one of the most affordable options in the category with a free plan covering 5 hours of transcription per month.',
