('notta',
 'Notta',
 'Fast AI transcription and meeting notes for voice and video across 104 languages',
 'Notta is an AI transcription and meeting assistant built for international teams and anyone who regularly processes audio or video content in multiple languages. The platform transcribes audio files, video files, and live meetings in 104 languages at up to 10 times the speed of real-time for uploaded recordings. Notta attends meetings as a bot on Zoom, Google Meet, and Microsoft Teams, or can transcribe audio directly from a phone call using the mobile app. The AI summary extracts action items, key topics, and a structured overview from the transcript. Notta''s strength is breadth: it handles podcast episodes, sales calls, lectures, interviews, and internal meetings with equal ease, making it useful for content teams that work across multiple audio formats. The collaborative notes feature lets teams highlight, annotate, and share specific sections of a transcript with colleagues.',
