('chorus',
 'Chorus',
 'Enterprise conversation intelligence platform by ZoomInfo for sales coaching',
 'Chorus is a conversation intelligence platform from ZoomInfo that analyses sales calls, demos, and customer meetings at enterprise scale. Every call is automatically recorded, transcribed, and scored against the team''s sales methodology - talk-to-listen ratio, competitor mentions, next steps confirmed, and questions asked. Managers use Chorus to review calls without sitting in on them, identify which reps are executing the playbook, and coach through specific call moments rather than generic feedback. The Deal Intelligence feature tracks which deals have slowing momentum based on call frequency and engagement patterns. Chorus integrates natively with Salesforce, syncing call activity, talk tracks, and deal signals to opportunity records. Because Chorus is part of the ZoomInfo platform, customers that already use ZoomInfo for prospecting data get direct enrichment from call intelligence back into their go-to-market workflows.',
