('modjo',
 'Modjo',
 'Revenue intelligence platform that turns sales call insights into team coaching',
 'Modjo is a revenue intelligence and sales conversation platform built for B2B sales teams that want to turn call recordings into systematic coaching. Unlike general meeting tools, Modjo is designed specifically around sales workflows: calls are automatically tagged by deal stage, rep, and topic, managers can leave timestamped comments on specific call moments, and team leaders can build a library of best-call examples for training new reps. The AI analyses calls against sales methodology markers - objection handling, discovery question depth, competitive positioning - and surfaces patterns across the team rather than just individual call metrics. Modjo integrates with HubSpot, Salesforce, Pipedrive, and most European CRM platforms, making it particularly popular with French and European B2B sales teams. The platform positions itself as a coaching tool rather than a surveillance tool, with emphasis on sharing calls that demonstrate good practice alongside calls that need improvement.',
