('airgram',
 'Airgram',
 'AI meeting assistant with pre-meeting agendas, real-time notes, and follow-up tasks',
 'Airgram is an AI meeting tool that covers the full meeting lifecycle - before, during, and after the call. Before a meeting, Airgram lets participants collaborate on a shared agenda so everyone arrives with aligned expectations. During the meeting, it transcribes in real time and lets participants highlight key moments. After the meeting, AI generates a structured summary with action items, decisions, and discussion points organised by agenda item. This agenda-first approach means Airgram summaries are structured around the meeting''s intended topics rather than following a generic template, producing output that is easier to use for follow-up. Airgram integrates with Google Calendar and Outlook for automatic meeting joining, and with Notion, Slack, and ClickUp for post-meeting task distribution. The collaborative note-taking features make it well suited to teams that want a single shared record of each meeting rather than individual notetakers producing separate versions.',
